Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.05,0:08:40.02,Normal,Kurumu,0,0,0,,Tsukune!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.80,0:08:43.99,Normal,Yukari,0,0,0,,Tsukune-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.53,0:08:47.05,Normal,Kurumu,0,0,0,,Bạn còn làm gì vậy? Tới đây nào!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.38,0:08:51.62,Normal,Tsukune,0,0,0,,Moka-san, đi thôi!
